      Myo Hub.waitForMyo()
      Wait for a Myo to become paired.

      This method blocks indefinitely until a Myo is found.
      Myo Hub.waitForMyo(int timeoutMs)
      Wait for a Myo to become paired, or time out after timeoutMs milliseconds.

      If timeoutMs is zero, this method blocks indefinitely until a Myo is found.
